Definition: a sin said to be inherited by all descendants of Adam
Example: Adam and Eve committed the original sin when they ate the forbidden fruit in the Garden of Eden
Synonyms: actual_sin, sin, noun, communication, religious_doctrine, a, said, to, be, inherited, by, all, descendants, of, Adam, and, Eve, committed, the, original, when, they, ate, forbidden, fruit, in, Garden, Eden
Category: noun.act
